---
title: Creamy Easy Chicken and Mushroom Risotto with Buttery Panko Topping
description: Let us introduce you to risotto made easy, using Uncle Ben's pre-made risotto! Miso broth concentrate packs a flavour punch in this umami-rich rice full of earthy mushrooms, creamy goat cheese and savoury Parmesan cheese, all topped with juicy chicken!
